LogEmailer v1.0.0

LogEmailer is protected by GNU General Public License for more information please refer to LICENSE.txt.

Windows Installation\Running:
1.  Download LogEmailer from https://github.com/jbb005/LogEmailer
2.  You must have at least JRE (Java Runtime Environment) on your system, this can be found at: http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/index.html
3.  You must set the PATH system variable for JRE this can be found at: http://www.java.com/en/download/help/path.xml
4.  Edit database.properties and logLocations.txt to desired settings.
5.  Open command prompt change to LogEmailer directory
6.  Enter command java -jar dist\LogEmailer to execute.

Mac Installation/Running:
1.  Download LogEmailer from https://github.com/jbb005/LogEmailer
2.  You must have at least JRE (Java Runtime Environment) on your system, this can be found at: http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/index.html
3.  Edit database.properties and logLocations.txt to desired settings.
4.  Open command prompt change to LogEmailer directory
5.  Enter command java -jar dist\LogEmailer to execute.

